<h2>Depositing data</h2>
<p>You can deposit your research data securely online in EASY by clicking the button 'New deposit' at the upper right corner of this page. If you don't have an account yet, please register yourself first.</p>
<p>DANS stores the data in a permanent and sustainable manner, according to the guidelines of the international Data Seal of Approval. The data will be made available to other researchers under the conditions you specified. See the general <a class="external" href="http://www.dans.knaw.nl/en/content/dans-licence-agreement-deposited-data" target="_blank">Licence agreement</a> for more juridical information about depositing data at DANS. You'll find practical instructions on depositing data per discipline under 'New deposit', or on the <a class="external" href="http://www.dans.knaw.nl/en/content/data-archive/depositing-data" target="_blank">DANS website.<br /></a></p>
